        "id": "forest_l4",
        "speakerMode": "narrator",
        "lineType": "auto",
        "text": "花瓣落在船头，我只想看看桃林尽头藏着什么。",
        "autoNextMs": 1600,
        "voiceTrack": "inner"
      }
    ],
